# Plan Tracking

Before implementation work, read `APP_PLAN.md`.

- Use `APP_PLAN.md` as the source of truth for pending work and priorities.
- Focus on making the app work beautifully on local laptop/simulator and physical iPhone first.
- Do not prioritize App Store readiness unless the user explicitly asks for it.
- When a task is completed and verified, update its row in `APP_PLAN.md` to `Ready` and check it off.
- Add a dated note to the `Progress Log` for completed or meaningfully advanced work.
